title: Standing Overhead Military Barbell Shoulder Press
description: Standing Overhead Military Barbell Shoulder Press Equipment required Barbell / EZ-Bar Primary muscle group(s) Position a barbell on a squat rack at shoulder height. Brace your core throughout the movement. Step underneath the barbell and grab onto it with shoulder-width hand placement. Step back with the barbell.
related_exercises: Dumbbell Biceps Curl to Shoulder Press
